    </ThingDef>

    <!-- Mirror Armor -->

    <ThingDef ParentName="MFS_HeavyArmorBase">
        <defName>MFS_MirrorArmor</defName>
        <label>mirror armor</label>
        <description>Named after its shining nature, mirror armor provides great protection against most forms of danger. A chainmail shirt attached with plates of metal to follow the joints, giving defense without causing discomfort. Still, it is one of the heaviest types of armor used in southern city states and is less suitable for long distance travel.</description>
